ng%20to%20two%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal.%20One%20of%20those%20people%20said%20Maven%20was%20targeting%20a%20%24150%20million%20raise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity%20firm%20StepStone%20Group%20is%20set%20to%20lead%20the%20round%2C%20per%20two%20sources%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaven%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaven-ipo-chrissy-farr-womens-health-startup-prediction-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacked%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20some%20colossal%20names%20in%20venture%20capital%2C%20including%20General%20Catalyst%2C%20Sequoia%2C%20and%20Oak%20HC%2FFT.%20Since%20its%202014%20launch%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-mom-help-maven-become-unicorn-women-health-startup-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24300%20million%20to%20bring%20virtual%20care%20to%20women%20and%20families.%20One%20person%20said%20the%20latest%20fundraising%20efforts%20value%20Maven%20at%20%241.7%20billion%2C%20a%20step%20up%20from%20its%20Series%20E%20valuation%20of%20%241.3%20billion.%20The%20startup%20raised%20that%20round%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fmaven-clinic-announces-90-million-series-e-round-of-funding-amidst-seismic-changes-in-womens-and-family-health-301676406.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2490%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20cash%20infusion%2C%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaven-ceo-kate-ryder-how-shes-making-healthcare-more-equitable-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egained%20traction%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20notching%20deals%20with%20employers%20and%20health%20plans%20to%20provide%20care%20across%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20from%20fertility%20to%20pregnancy%20to%20postpartum%20care%20and%20menopause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStepStone%20is