2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fbreast-cancer%2Fabout%2Fdense-breasts.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20developing%20breast%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20makes%20it%20harder%20for%20clinicians%20to%20spot%20cancer%20in%20a%20mammogram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20cases%20of%20high%20breast%20density%2C%20other%20screening%20methods%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdensebreast-info.org%2Fscreening-technologies%2Fcancer-detection-by-screening-method%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eultrasounds%20or%20MRIs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20can%20be%20more%20effective%20at%20detecting%20tumors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20and%20doctors%20have%20been%20campaigning%20for%20decades%20to%20include%20breast%20density%20in%20screenings%2C%20testifying%20to%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20and%20lawmakers.%20Their%20campaign%20culminated%20in%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20FDA%20this%20summer%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fradiation-emitting-products%2Fmammography-quality-standards-act-mqsa-and-mqsa-program%2Fimportant-information-final-rule-amend-mammography-quality-standards-act-mqsa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20rule%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c61f5c6-a34f-40f5-98c6-bb33fe3b2954%5C%22%3EWhy%20breast%20density%20makes%20cancer%20more%20likely%20and%20harder%20to%20spot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rule%20means%20that%20mammogram%20reports%20will%20now%20assess%20the%20ratio%20of%20fatty%20tissue%20to%20fibroglandular%20tissue.%20More%20fibroglandular%20tissue%20means%20a%20denser%20breast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDense%20breasts%20obscure%20tumors%20on%20a%20mammogram%20because%20the%20fibroglandular%20tissue%20%E2%80%94%20like%20cancer%20%E2%80%94%20looks%20white%20on%20the%20screen.%20Fatty%20tissue%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20appears%20black%2C%20gray%2C%20or%20colorless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20higher%20breast%20density%20also%20increases%20one's%20risk%20of%20developing%20breast%20cancer%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20exactly%20clear%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20mammogram%20image%20of%20cancer%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bnot%20dense%26quot%3B%20breast%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdense%26quot%3B%20breast.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6685a20d268f62ba18a75d21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20side-by-side%20mammogram%20image%20of%20cancer%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bnot%20dense%26quot%3B%20breast%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bdense%26quot%3B%20breast.%3Cp%3EDenseBreast-info%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rule%20does%20not%20mandate%20specific%20follow-ups%20or%20next%20steps%2C%20but%20providers%20should%20advise%20patients%20with%20dense%20breasts%20to%20explore%20further%20screening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b1652ef-be35-498f-8b2a-ba4a8c22629b%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20whose%20breast%20cancer%20went%20undetected%20spent%20years%20campaigning%20for%20this%20rule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20JoAnn%20Pushkin%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20educational%20resource%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdensebreast-info.org%2Ffor-patients%2F5-facts-you-should-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDenseBreast-info%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shared%20her%20late%20cancer%20diagnosis%20story%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-cancer-missed-dense-breasts-mammogram-screening-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPushkin%20had%20no%20apparent%20breast%20cancer%20risk%20factors.%20Her%20only%20family%20history%20was%20one%20aunt%20who'd%20had%20breast%20cancer.%20She%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcancer-prevention-lifestyle-changes-dietitian-advice-healthy-eating-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregularly%20exercised%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eate%20well%2C%20perfo