E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20globally%20televised%20debate%20offers%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20a%20former%20prosecutor%2C%20the%20chance%20to%20make%20her%20case%20and%20corner%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20whose%20felony%20convictions%2C%20outspoken%20backing%20for%20supporters%20convicted%20of%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20attack%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%20and%20frequent%20falsehoods%20all%20offer%20plenty%20of%20fertile%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20also%20indulged%20in%20personal%20attacks%20on%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20included%20racist%20and%20sexist%20insults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%2C%2059%2C%20who%20enjoys%20a%20significant%20advantage%20among%20women%20voters%20according%20to%20the%20most%20recent%20polls%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20press%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20reproductive%20rights%20after%20he%20made%20a%20number%20of%20seemingly%20contradictory%20comments%20recently%20on%20abortion%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%2078%2C%20will%20meanwhile%20try%20to%20corner%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20current%20vice-president%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20economy%2C%20immigration%2C%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ABC%20News%20debate%20is%20scheduled%20to%20last%20for%2090%20minutes%20and%20will%20be%20held%20without%20an%20audience.%20There%20are%20also%20some%20established%20rules%20for%20the%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20CANDIDATES%2C%20THE%20PREPARATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20is%20America's%20first%20female%2C%20Black%20and%20Indian-American%20Vice%20President.%20Ms%20Harris%20arrived%20in%20Philadelphia%20a%20day%20before%20the%20debate%20after%20isolating%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Pittsburgh%20for%20five%20days%20amid%20intense%20practice%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20team%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20a%20more%20relaxed%20approach%20ahead%20of%20his%20seventh%20presidential%20debate%2C%20choosing%20to%20arrive%20in%20Philadelphia%20just%20hours%20before%20and%20keeping%20his%20preparations%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20will%20certainly%20see%20a%20contrast%20in%20styles%20of%20both%20candidates%2C%20but%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20quiet%20one%20with%20the%20rules%20stating%20that%20the%20two%20candidates'%20microphones%20will%20be%20muted%20when%20they%20are%20not%20speaking.%20This%20was%20done%20on%20the%20Trump%20team's%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20part%20of%20six%20previous%20Presidential%20debates%2C%20this%20would%20be%20the%20first%20one%20for%20Kamala%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2090-minute%20debate%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20National%20Constitution%20Center%20in%20Philadelphia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725992880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fq9e3nlb4_donald-trump-kamala-harris-reuters_625x300_10_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-donald-trump-kamala-harris-face-off-ahead-of-2024-us-elections-6536196%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20crucial%20US%20Presidential%20debate%20being%20hosted%20by%20ABC%20Networks%20globally.%20The%20presidential%20debate%20comes%20exactly%208%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20election%20day%20across%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-presidential-debate-donald-trump-kamala-harris-face-off-ahead-of-2024-us-elections-6536196%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Have%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Kamala%20Harris%20ever%20met%3F%20'I%20have%20a%20photo%20of%20her...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725992848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113237652%2Cimgsi