ent%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fphonepe-liquid-group-tie-up-to-expand-upi-qr-payment-service-in-singapore-124091001341_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fphonepe-liquid-group-tie-up-to-expand-upi-qr-payment-service-in-singapore-124091001341_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fphonepe-liquid-group-tie-up-to-expand-upi-qr-payment-service-in-singapore-124091001341_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Loyal%20Workers%20Being%20Sidelined'%3A%20Another%20Senior%20Haryana%20Leader%20Quits%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20setback%20for%20the%20BJP%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Haryana%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20has%20quit%20the%20party%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20prioritising%20leaders%20who%20have%20never%20worked%20for%20the%20organisation%20over%20those%20who%20have%20been%20loyal%20to%20it.%20The%20resignation%20of%20Santosh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20former%20deputy%20speaker%2C%20follows%20a%20string%20of%20similar%20actions%20by%20leaders%20upset%20over%20being%20denied%20a%20ticket%20in%20the%20two%20lists%20of%20candidates%20declared%20by%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Haryana%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Ms%20Yadav%20was%20seeking%20a%20ticket%20from%20the%20Ateli%20Assembly%20seat%2C%20which%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20Union%20Minister%20Rao%20Inderjit%20Singh's%20daughter%20Aarti%20Singh%20Rao%20in%20the%20second%20list%20of%2021%20candidates%20released%20by%20the%20BJP%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20the%20president%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Ms%20Yadav%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%20that%20her%20dedication%20to%20the%20party%20had%20been%20unwavering%20and%20she%20had%20followed%20its%20principles%20and%20policies%20in%20every%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20with%20great%20sorrow%2C%20I%20have%20to%20say%20that%20the%20party%20is%20neglecting%20those%20people%20who%20struggled%20for%20it%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20worked%20with%20devotion%20and%20made%20a%20significant%20contribution%20in%20strengthening%20the%20party.%20Such%20dedicated%20workers%20are%20being%20sidelined%20and%20priority%20is%20being%20given%20to%20those%20persons%20who%20neither%20worked%20for%20the%20party%20nor%20for%20the%20citizens%20of%20their%20assembly%20constituency.%20This%20situation%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20and%20it%20is%20spreading%20disappointment%20and%20dissatisfaction%20among%20the%20party%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Yadav's%20resignation%20from%20all%20party%20posts%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20a%20fellow%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Haryana%20BJP%2C%20GL%20Sharma%20joined%20the%20Congress%20with%20more%20than%20250%20BJP%20workers%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20former%20Haryana%20minister%20Bachan%20Singh%20Arya%20had%20resigned%20from%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20field%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20rebel%20Ram%20Kumar%20Gautam%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20party%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20from%20the%20Safidon%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigh-Profile%20Exits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Arya's%20resignation%20followed%20the%20exit%20of%20two%20Haryana%20ministers%20-%20Energy%20Minister%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Chautala%20and%20Minister%20of%20State%20(Independent%20Charge)%20for%20Social%20Justice%20Bishamber%20Singh%20Valmiki%20-%20and%20MLA%20Lakshman%20Napa%2C%20who%20were%20denied%20tickets.%20Key%20OBC%20leader%20Karan%20Dev%20Kamboj%20also%20resigned%20from%20all%20posts%20in%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20loss%20of%20Mr%20Chautala%2C%2079%2C%20can%20hurt%20the%20party%20as%20he%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal%2C%20one%20of%20Haryana's%20tallest%20leaders%2C%20who%20served%20as%20chief%20minister%20twice%20and%20was%20also%20a%20deputy%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Ms%20Yadav%2C%20some%20of%20the%20leaders%20had%20claimed%20that%20loyalists%20were%20not%20being%20valued%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20need%20loyalists%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamboj%20had%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20party%20was%20rewarding%20leaders%20who%20had%20joined%20it%20recently%20while%20ignoring%20those%20who%20had%20served%20it%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Lotus%20Can%20Be%20Given%20Only%20To%201%20Person'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20rebellion%2C%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20had%20said%20last%20week%20that%20speculation%20over%20changing%20candidates%20should%20end%20as%20there%20was%20no%20scope%20for%20doing%20so.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20wants%20a%20ticket%2C%20but%20the%20'lotus'%20(BJP's%20symbol)%20can%20be%20given%20to%20only%20one%20person...%20It%20is%20natural%20for%20ticket-seekers%20to%20get%20angry.%20But%20they%20will%20be%20persuaded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20all%2090%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%205%20and%20counting%20will%20be%20held%20on%20October%208.%20The%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20to%20retain%20its%20hold%20on%20power%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20state%2C%20which%20it%20has%20ruled%20since%202014%2C%20but%20is%20facing%20a%20challenge%20from%20a%20resurgent%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20two%20lists%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20declared%20the%20names%20of%2088%20candidates%20so%20far%2C%20including%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20from%20the%20Ladwa%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725987900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fdn9dgqlg_santo