eral%20agency%20comes%20after%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20High%20Court%20quashed%20its%20case%20and%20charge%20sheet%20against%20Abdullah%20and%20some%20others%20on%20August%2014%20saying%20the%20offence%20of%20money%20laundering%20was%20not%20made%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20the%20ED%20to%20%26quot%3Bcanvass%26quot%3B%20its%20case%20before%20a%20local%20court%20seeking%20addition%20of%20fresh%20IPC%20sections%20and%20if%20it%20decides%20to%20frame%20charges%20against%20Abdullah%20and%20five%20others%20for%20any%20of%20the%20scheduled%20offences%2C%20it%20shall%20be%20open%20for%20the%20ED%20to%20register%20a%20fresh%20case%20and%20launch%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20as%20per%20the%20sources%2C%20filed%20this%20high%20court-directed%20application%20recently%20stating%20that%20the%20CBI%20%26quot%3Binadvertently%20missed%2Ffailed%20to%20specifically%20incorporate%2Fmention%20the%20said%20offence%20under%20Section%20411%20and%20424%20of%20IPC%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20assembly%20polls%20are%20being%20held%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%2086-year-old%20Abdullah's%20party%2C%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%2C%20is%20in%20the%20fray%20along%20with%20other%20parties.%20Abdullah%20is%20the%20president%20of%20NC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20in%20its%20application%2C%20has%20requested%20the%20Srinagar%20court%20to%20frame%20fresh%20charges%20against%20the%20accused%20under%20the%20two%20stated%20sections%20saying%20it%20(Srinagar%20court)%20was%20vested%20with%20wide%20powers%20under%20section%20216%20of%20CrPC%20to%20%26quot%3Badd%2Famend%26quot%3B%20charges%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20can%20be%20exercised%20in%20appropriate%20cases%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20has%20been%20questioned%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20agency%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20attached%20assets%2