aponised%20--%20in%20small%2C%20potent%20doses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20doing%20this%20through%20a%20polished%20film%2C%20they%20maintain%20dignity%20and%20control%20while%20still%20appearing%20relatable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20likened%20the%20video%2C%20shot%20by%20filmmaker%20Will%20Warr%20in%20the%20Norfolk%20countryside%20of%20eastern%20England%20where%20the%20family%20has%20a%20home%2C%20to%20a%20Hollywood%20trailer%20for%20the%20Instagram%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20assessed%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20intimate%20portrayal%20of%20royal%20family%20since%20(Queen%20Elizabeth%20II)%20invited%20a%20fly-on-the-wall%20documentary%20crew%20into%20her%20home%20in%201969%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%2040%20years%20of%20covering%20the%20Royal%20Family%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20Catherine's%20video.%20It's%20a%20first%20for%20the%20royals%2C%26quot%3B%20veteran%20photographer%20Arthur%20Edwards%20wrote%20in%20The%20Sun%20tabloid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENarrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENewspapers%20sought%20to%20decode%20the%20meaning%20behind%20the%20soft-focus%20scenes%20of%20the%20young%20family%20seeking%20solace%20in%20nature%20and%20enjoying%20each%20other's%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20saw%20in%20it%20a%20clear%20sign%20that%20the%20princess%2C%20who%20will%20be%20queen%20when%20William%20succeeds%20his%20father%20King%20Charles%20III%2C%20was%20carefully%20attempting%20to%20control%20the%20narrative%20of%20her%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20the%20one%20in%20the%20driving%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20The%20Times%2C%20while%20Jennie%20Bond%2C%20a%20former%20BBC%20royal%20correspondent%2C%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bputting%20down%20her%20marker%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20how%20she%20wants%20to%20communicate%20with%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Sky%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20this%20she%20has%20shown%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20straight%20with%20people%2C%20she%20wants%20to%20be%20direct%2C%20she%20wants%20the%20message%20to%20be%20quite%20simple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20largely%20positive%20public%20response%20to%20the%20video%20comes%20after%20criticism%20of%20Kensington%20Palace%2C%20the%20couple's%20private%20office%2C%20and%20its%20handling%20of%20communications%20about%20Kate's%20illness%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20ran%20riot%2C%20especially%20online%2C%20after%20Kate%20--%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20photographed%20women%20--%20was%20not%20seen%20in%20public%20for%20months%20following%20abdominal%20surgery%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20attempt%20to%20silence%20the%20rumours%20failed%20in%20March%2C%20when%20a%20family%20portrait%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20palace%2C%20was%20found%20to%20have%20been%20digitally%20altered%2C%20fuelling%20the%20chatter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKate's%20announcement%20that%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20form%20of%20cancer%20followed%20soon%20afterwards%2C%20prompting%20widespread%20public%20sympathy%20and%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorkowski%20said%20the%20latest%20video%2C%20and%20Kate's%20commentary%20accompanying%20it%2C%20showed%20the%20royal%20family%20was%20now%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20front%20foot%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20lost%20control%20of%20the%20cancer%20narrative%20by%20staying%20silent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20they%20learnt%20from%20earlier%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20senior%20royals%2C%20William%20and%20Kate%20have%20a%20strong%20social%20media%20presence%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20essential%20to%20maintain%20the%20British%20royal%20family's%20relevance%20and%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20late%20queen's%20death%2C%20Charles%20has%20faced%20vocal%20protests%20from%20republicans%20who%20wa