%20two%20sides%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20were%20replaced%20by%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20escalated%20after%20three%20Maldivian%20deputy%20ministers%20made%20controversial%20remarks%20regarding%20India%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%20Foreign%20Ministry%20distanced%20itself%20from%20their%20remarks%2C%20saying%20they%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20views%20of%20the%20Male%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20junior%20ministers%20were%20suspended%2C%20and%20two%20of%20them%20-%20Mariyam%20Shiuna%20and%20Malsha%20Shareef%20-%20resigned%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20key%20maritime%20neighbours%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%20and%20the%20overall%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20including%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20defence%20and%20security%2C%20witnessed%20an%20upward%20trajectory%20under%20the%20previous%20government%20led%20by%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725985020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fii54qd8o_narendra-modi-maldives-president-mohamed-muizzu-modi-muizzu_625x300_10_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldivies-president-mohamed-muizzu-to-visit-india-soon-2-ministers-resign-amid-strained-ties-6533861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20will%20travel%20to%20India%20on%20an%20official%20visit%20%26quot%3Bvery%20soon%26quot%3B%2C%20his%20spokesperson%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmaldivies-president-mohamed-muizzu-to-visit-india-soon-2-ministers-resign-amid-strained-ties-65338