2%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-amends-certain-rules-related-to-amalgamations-under-companies-law-124091001244_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Afghanistan%20Fiasco%20Spells%20End%20For%20Noida%20Venue%3F%20India%20Pace%20Great%20May%20Decide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMatch%20referee%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Javagal%20Srinath%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F396-javagal-srinath-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJavagal%20Srinath%3C%2Fa%3E's%20report%20on%20the%20preparedness%20of%20Shaheed%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vijay%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F57387-vijay-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVijay%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pathik%20Sports%20complex%20in%20Greater%20Noida%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20deciding%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20venue%20which%20is%20under%20the%20scanner%20after%20the%20one-off%20Test%20between%20Afghanistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%20failed%20to%20get%20underway%20on%20successive%20days.%20For%20once%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%2C%20which%20often%20becomes%20the%20favourite%20whipping%20boy%2C%20isn't%20responsible%20for%20the%20mess.%20The%20'home%20board'%20is%20the%20Afghanistan%20Cricket%20Board%2C%20which%20selected%20a%20familiar%20and%20cost-effective%20venue%20despite%20being%20offered%20the%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Green%20Park%20in%20Kanpur%20as%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20isn't%20involved%20in%20this%20Test%20match.%20It%20was%20the%20Afghanistan%20Cricket%20Board's%20choice%20and%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20Authority%20was%20supposed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20international%20standard%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20hasn't%20hosted%20any%20of%20its%20domestic%20games%20here%20since%202019%20(Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy)%20and%20is%20unlikely%20to%20host%20one%20in%20near%20or%20distant%20future%20in%20these%20substandard%20conditions%2C%20if%20sources%20are%20to%20be%20believed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%2C%20for%20one%2C%20would%20follow%20the%20standard%20protocol%20for%20any%20given%20international%20venue%20where%20the%20match%20referee's%20report%20decide%20the%20further%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20single%20ball%20could%20be%20bowled%20in%20the%20first%20two%20days%20and%20with%20a%20steady%20downpour%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20reducing%20the%20chances%20of%20play%20on%20third%20day%2C%20Srinath%20will%20have%20to%20assess%20the%20drainage%20conditions%20of%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20are%20not%20at%20par%20with%20other%20international%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20bright%20sunshine%20across%20two%20days%20but%20one%20heavy%20spell%20of%20shower%2C%20in%20the%20preceding%20evening%2C%20was%20enough%20to%20play%20spoilsport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20adequate%20super%20sopper%20or%20enough%20ground%20cover%20to%20protect%20the%20outfield%2C%20or%20for%20that%20matter%20the%20lack%20of%20adequately%20trained%20ground%20staff%2C%20there%20are%20problems%20aplenty%20with%20this%20venue%2C%20which%20isn't%20directly%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20BCCI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20ICC%20'Pitch%20and%20Outfield%20Monitoring%20Process'%20that%20came%20into%20effect%20in%20November%202023%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20each%20Match%2C%20the%20Match%20Referee%20(Srinath%20in%20this%20case)%20will%20complete%20a%20Pitch%20and%20Outfield%20Report%20Form%20and%20send%20it%20to%20the%20ICC%20Senior%20Cricket%20Operations%20Manager.%26quot%3B%20The%20'Pitch%20and%20Outfield%20Report%20Form'%20will%20be%20compiled%20using%20the%20guidelines%20for%20rating%20pitches%20and%20outfields%20and%2C%20where%20required%2C%20will%20include%20comments%20on%20the%20pitch%20and%20outfield%20from%20the%20captains%20of%20the%20two%20teams%20who%20played%20and%20the%20umpires%20who%20officiated%20in%20the%20relevant%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20note%20the%20kind%20of%20comments%20given%20by%20New%20Zealand%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tim%20Southee%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1032-tim-southee-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETim%20Southee%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%2014%20days%20of%20receipt%2C%20the%20ICC%20senior%20cricket%20operations%20manager%20will%20forward%20the%20'Pitch%20and%20Outfield%20Report%20Form'%20to%20the%20home%20board%2C%20with%20a%20copy%20to%20the%20visiting%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20senior%20cricket%20operations%20manager%20will%20advise%20the%20home%20board%20on%20any%20demerit%20points%20that%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20a%20host%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ICC%20clause%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20conditions%20are%20such%20that%20the%20Match%20Referee%20has%20cause%20to%20rate%20the%20pitch%20and%2For%20outfield%20Unsatisfactory%20or%20Unfit%2C%20a%20corresponding%20number%20of%20Demerit%20Points%20will%20be%20imposed%20upon%20the%20Host%20Venue%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20guidelines%20for%20rating%20pitches%20and%20outfields.%26quot%3B%20Demerit%20Points%20will%20remain%20active%20for%20a%20rolling%20five-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20venue%20accumulates%20a%20total%20of%20six%20(6)%20or%20more%20demerit%20points%2C%20its%20accreditation%20to%20host%20international%20matches%20will%20be%20suspended%20for%20a%20period%20of%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20one%20goes%20through%20ICC%20rules%2C%20for%20a%20single%20Test%20match%2C%20if%20both%20pitch%20and%20outfield%20are%20deemed%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B%20by%20match%20referee%2C%20then%20it%20would%20get%20three%20demerit%20points%20and%20it%20would%20take%20one%20more%20such%20game%20to%20get%20the%20venue%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20onus%20will%20thus%20be%20on%20the%20Afghanistan%20Cricket%20Board%20to%20see%20whether%20they%20would%20want%20to%20continue%20hosting%20matches%20at%20such%20a%20venue%2C%20which%20could%20get%20suspended%20in%20near%20future%20due%20to%20its%20poor%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20facelift%20of%20gigantic%20proportions%20can't%20be%20done%20by%20the%20local%20authorities%20and%20they%20would%20need%20the%20BCCI's%20deep%20pockets%20to%20make%20it%20at%20least%20a%20palatable%20domestic%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725981060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9t4lctr8_greater-noida-venue_625x300_10_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafghanistan-test-fiasco-spells-end-for-greater-noida-venue-in-cricket-india-pace-great-may-have-final-word-6534982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20the%20Afghanistan%20Cricket%20Board's%20choice%20and%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20Authority%20was%20supposed%20to%20provide%20them%20with%20international%20standard%20facilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fafghanistan-test-fiasco-spells-end-for-greater-noida-venue-in-cricket-india-pace-great-may-have-final-word-6534982%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Open%20champion%20and%20Ryder%20Cup%20star%20ends%20deal%20with%20Grenfell%20insulation%20firm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725981060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-shane-lowry-kingspan_6681312.jpg%3F20240910160756%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fshane-lowry-golfer-ends-deal-with-kingspan-days-after-end-of-grenfell-inquiry-13212420%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Irish%20golfer%20Shane%20Lowry%20has%20ended%20his%20partnership%20with%20Kingspan%20after%20it%20was%20found%20to%20have%20shown%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20disregard%26quot%3B%20for%20fire%20safety%20before%20the%20Grenfell%20Tower%20tragedy.%22%2C%22