ns%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20September%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20talk%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreen%20wave%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20constituency%2C%20Mr%20Tarigami%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20at%20all.%20Since%201996%2C%20which%20was%20the%20peak%20of%20militancy%2C%20despite%20all%20odds%20and%20difficulties%2C%20when%20our%20cadres%20were%20being%20killed%2C%20we%20campaigned%2C%20defied%20the%20writ%20of%20militants%20and%20succeeded%20in%20winning%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20people.%20As%20far%20as%20today%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20is%20not%20something%20new%3B%20people%20are%20mistaken%2C%20as%20if%20Jamaat%20has%20taken%20a%20U-turn%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20Going%20through%20their%20history%20will%20tell%20you%20this%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20jail%20for%2021%20months%20in%201972%20after%20the%20plebiscite%20movement%20was%20banned%20and%2C%20when%20I%20was%20released%2C%20I%20was%20received%20in%20my%20constituency%20by%20a%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20MLA%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tarigami%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Jamaat%20had%20won%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%201983%20and%20also%20in%201987%20-%20an%20election%20that%20he%20termed%20%26quot%3Bmassively%20rigged%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20in%20three%20phases%20between%20September%2018%20and%20October%201%2C%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%2090%20Assembly%20seats%20will%20take%20place%20on%20October%208.%20This%20is%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20first%20Assembly%20election%20since%202014%20as%20well%20as%20the%20first%20since%20the%20removal%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20was%20abrogated%20on%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20and%20the%20state%20was%20also%20divided%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh.%20The%20resto